review:
I foud this while browsing in Toys R Us for $20 and you would never guess my surprise when I actually opened it. I thought: &quot;for $20 and 300 peices (especially BIONICLE peices) this is a deal regardless of its contents, so, let's see what's inside...&quot;

I had no Idea that I would get so many parts plus 4/6 vahki, 2 masks of time (don't ask why) and two surprisingly unspectacular disks of time which are actually faithful to the story since the mask was forged from a disk of the six infused elements.

If you somehow find this still sealed and at a decent price, buy it, without hesitation, if you are a fan, collector, or a kid who needs more parts, buy it!
